#: ../../apm/apm-data-links/apm-create-data-links.rst:92
msgid "Enter the Splunk instance fully qualified domain name (FQDN) and port of your Splunk instance for the :strong:`URL`. For example, you might enter :strong:`https://<yourHostname>.splunkcloud.com:443` for a Splunk Cloud Platform instance. You might also specify the FQDN and port for a Splunk Enterprise instance you have access to."
